              <span id="reviewTextContainer2894758124" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9069140397622030069">Dear Sweet Vincent. I love him v much and he was truly a beautiful writer! Words, paint, art. I feel like I got to know him so much...I miss him! All heart. &lt;3</span>

          </span>
        </div>


